{
  "stem": "4693.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because there was much more than 10% percent of Jews on the boat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Once we arrived in Australia, the problem was over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I never heard about the Jewish, non-Jewish problem in Australia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But on the boat, this guy was making plenty of intrigues.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he knows that I was on high position before in UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I told him once off and it didn't help.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And when we arrived in Melbourne-- because this was the end, where the ship finished-- he came to me and I want to say goodbye.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And I told him, look, piss off.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I told him, look, I will see to it that you'll never work for IRO again.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And, really, I wrote a report to the headquarters of IRO, to people who I knew.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I was later informed that he was sent on the first available plane to Canada.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He never worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I am coming to the period in Australia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "I have to say, there is one thing for sure-- it was not a day from my arrival in Australia that I regretted it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "The first period when I arrived here, I worked as a laborer for half a year.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I had some money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I had some money to stay, but I want to learn the conditions here before doing anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I didn't have much money, but I had some.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Then after a half a year, my wife, in Germany, I-- because I was busy all the time and going from one meeting in one part of Germany to another meeting in another part of Germany-- and my wife was supposed to learn-- HIAS had courses, learn how to make shirts.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I thought that we decided to make shirts, with her as a specialist.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
